### Variables
@baseUrl = http://postgrado-fiis.test/api
@token = REEMPLAZAR_CON_TOKEN_REAL
@bearerToken = REEMPLAZAR_CON_SANCTUM_TOKEN

###
### 1. Listar diplomados activos
GET {{baseUrl}}/diplomado/programs
Accept: application/json

###
### 2. Registrar inscripción (boleta)
POST {{baseUrl}}/diplomado/register
Content-Type: application/json
Accept: application/json

{
  "program_id": 1,
  "academic_period_id": 1,
  "full_name": "Juan Carlos Pérez García",
  "dni": "12345678",
  "birthdate": "1990-05-15",
  "phone": "987654321",
  "email": "juan.perez@ejemplo.com",
  "address": "Av. Universitaria 1234",
  "city": "Lima",
  "university": "Universidad Nacional de Ingeniería",
  "academic_degree": "bachelor",
  "career": "Ingeniería de Sistemas",
  "voucher_type": "boleta"
}

###
### 3. Registrar inscripción (factura)
POST {{baseUrl}}/diplomado/register
Content-Type: application/json
Accept: application/json

{
  "program_id": 1,
  "academic_period_id": 1,
  "full_name": "María López Torres",
  "dni": "87654321",
  "birthdate": "1985-09-20",
  "phone": "912345678",
  "email": "maria.lopez@empresa.com",
  "address": "Jr. Comercio 567",
  "city": "Arequipa",
  "university": "Universidad Católica Santa María",
  "academic_degree": "graduate",
  "career": "Administración de Empresas",
  "voucher_type": "factura",
  "razon_social": "Empresa Consulting SAC",
  "ruc": "20123456789",
  "fiscal_address": "Av. Industrial 456, Arequipa",
  "invoice_email": "facturacion@empresa.com"
}

###
### 4. Registrar inscripción (egresado)
POST {{baseUrl}}/diplomado/register
Content-Type: application/json
Accept: application/json

{
  "program_id": 1,
  "academic_period_id": 1,
  "full_name": "Carlos Mamani Quispe",
  "dni": "45678901",
  "birthdate": "1998-03-10",
  "phone": "965432187",
  "email": "carlos.mamani@gmail.com",
  "address": "Calle Los Álamos 789",
  "city": "Cusco",
  "university": "Universidad Andina del Cusco",
  "academic_degree": "egresado",
  "career": "Ingeniería de Sistemas e Informática",
  "voucher_type": "boleta"
}

###
### 5. Consultar estado de inscripción por token
GET {{baseUrl}}/diplomado/registration/{{token}}
Accept: application/json

###
### 6. Consultar estado — token inválido (espera 404)
GET {{baseUrl}}/diplomado/registration/token-inexistente-xyz
Accept: application/json

###
# =====================================================
# PORTAL DEL ESTUDIANTE DIPLOMADO (requiere auth:sanctum)
# =====================================================

###
### 7. Mi diplomado — estado de matrícula y resumen de pagos
GET {{baseUrl}}/portal/diplomado/me
Accept: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{bearerToken}}

###
### 8. Mis cargos — listado pagados y pendientes
GET {{baseUrl}}/portal/diplomado/charges
Accept: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{bearerToken}}

###
### 9. Opciones de pago para una cuota específica
GET {{baseUrl}}/portal/diplomado/charges/1/payment-options
Accept: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{bearerToken}}
